title: 01/17/22 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 01/17/22 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps all the action from Wild Card week in the NFL. Should the Cowboys move on from Mike McCarthy? Long time caller Shea in Irving makes his long awaited return to react to the Cowboys loss. Patriots Insider Tom Curran discusses whether New England had a successful season. And Carson Palmer helps preview the Rams/Cardinals game tonight. Who wins?
